      <notesStmt>
        <note>Title from colophon (f. 10r) and cover page (f. 1r). Cover page reads: atha śarabhakavacaprārambhaḥ patreṁ 10.</note>
        <note>Written 9 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>Good condition. Paper very brown. Mistakes covered over with yellow.</note>
        <note>Begins: śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ śrīsarasvatyai namaḥ śrīgurubhyo namaḥ śrīdevyuvāca[.] sarvajña sarvamantrajña sarvācārya śiva pabho. śārabhaṁ kavacaṁ divyaṁ sarvarakṣākaraṁ paraṁ (verse 1). vajrapañjaranāmākhyaṁ vada me karuṇākara. śrīśiva uvāca. kathyāmi śṛṇu te devi sarvarakṣākaraṁ paraṁ (verse 2).</note>
        <note>Ends: prāgānanobhi vṛddhau tu sarveṣvīśānadiṅmukhaḥ yojayet kavacaṁ nityaṁ trikālaṁ dhyȧnapūrvakaṁ (verse 109). sarvasiddhim evāpnoti sahasā sādhakottamaḥ. devadevamahādevaśivakāruṇyavāridhe (verse 110). pāhi māṁ praṇataṁ svāmin prasīda satataṁ mama.</note>
      </notesStmt>
